Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.06,0:22:18.66,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}The words will make you out 'n' out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.67,0:22:23.99,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}I spend the day your way
