Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.12,0:22:57.69,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}Call it morning driving thru the sound and in and out the valley
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:23:00.35,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}In and around the lake
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.40,0:23:05.51,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}Mountains come out of the sky and they stand there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.48,0:23:12.27,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}One mile over we'll be there and we'll see you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.90,0:23:18.70,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}Ten true summers we'll be there and laughing too
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.39,0:23:27.00,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}Twenty four before my love you'll see I'll be there with you
